<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-07-24T12:29:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-07-24T12:29:00-05:00" n="323" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d323">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.51/251</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Cuba</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Gonzales</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-07-24T12:00:00-05:29">
                                        <hi rend="italic">July 24, 1917, noon.</hi>
                                    </date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>President Menocal has vetoed bill granting authority to make issue
                                30,000,000-dollar loan. Cause of veto certain restrictive
                                provisions, one requiring advertisements for bids and also
                                elimination by Congress of certain taxes including stamp tax
                                proposed by President for interest and amortization.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>